WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.366 --> 00:00:03.000
Grandpa, I also want to be your granddaughter-in-law.

2
00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.666
But he broke his promise and he never accepted me

3
00:00:05.666 --> 00:00:07.433
Now this Lin Nuannuan appears

4
00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:09.400
He won't even let me into my uncle's house

5
00:00:09.900 --> 00:00:11.400
Such a nice girl

6
00:00:11.533 --> 00:00:13.100
Broken promises are blind

7
00:00:14.266 --> 00:00:17.166
If I hadn't taken the medicine you prescribed all these years

8
00:00:17.166 --> 00:00:19.966
My old bones are long gone

9
00:00:20.133 --> 00:00:21.866
I see the car is messy

10
00:00:22.066 --> 00:00:24.033
I just want to hope that our uncle will inform us.

11
00:00:24.100 --> 00:00:26.033
I think so too

12
00:00:28.166 --> 00:00:31.500
Grandpa won't let my precious granddaughter

13
00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:33.633
Can you talk?

14
00:00:34.766 --> 00:00:37.300
Grandpa Nuannuan is a good person

15
00:00:37.566 --> 00:00:39.766
You can't say that about him

16
00:00:39.966 --> 00:00:41.666
He likes Lin Nuannuan

17
00:00:41.666 --> 00:00:43.366
Grandpa, it's getting late.

18
00:00:43.366 --> 00:00:45.166
Go back to your room early to take medicine and rest

19
00:00:45.900 --> 00:00:48.000
Sister Jin takes grandpa back to the room

